            "id": "b4a37c0",
            "elType": "widget",
            "settings": {
              "html": "\n<div style=\"background:#08122A;padding:3.75rem 3.75rem 7rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.15);position:relative;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <div style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(196,154,42,0.03) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(196,154,42,0.03) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:60px 60px;pointer-events:none;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"padding:0;position:relative;z-index:1;\">\n    \n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:1.8rem;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:1px;background:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\"></div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;\">Core Track \u00b7 12 Months</span></div>\n    <h1 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,5rem);font-weight:300;line-height:1.04;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 1.8rem;\">From clinical insight<br>to validated product.</h1>\n    <p style=\"font-size:1rem;line-height:1.7;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);max-width:600px;margin:1.5rem 0 0;\">Our flagship program for healthcare, biotech, and medical device innovators. If you've identified a real clinical problem and are serious about solving it \u2014 with rigour, regulatory awareness, and a plan to reach patients \u2014 this is your track.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#F7F3EC;padding:7rem 0;\">\n  <div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:3.75rem 3.75rem 7rem;\">\n\n    <!-- Stats bar -->\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1rem;margin-bottom:5rem;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align:center;padding:2rem;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;\"><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;\">12</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;margin-top:4px;\">Month Program</div></div><div style=\"text-align:center;padding:2rem;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;\"><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;\">10</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;margin-top:4px;\">Seats Available</div></div><div style=\"text-align:center;padding:2rem;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;\"><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;\">4</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;margin-top:4px;\">Structured Phases</div></div><div style=\"text-align:center;padding:2rem;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;\"><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;\">500+</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;margin-top:4px;\">Bed Hospital Access</div></div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Is this for you -->\n    <p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">Is This For You?</p>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;margin-bottom:5rem;\">\n      <div>\n        <h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 1rem;\">\u2713 This track is built for you if\u2026</h3>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#3B6D11;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You're a clinician, researcher, or engineer who has identified a specific, patient-validated clinical problem</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#3B6D11;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You want to build a medical device, diagnostic tool, digital health solution, or biotech product</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#3B6D11;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You're at idea, early research, or pre-prototype stage and need infrastructure to develop further</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#3B6D11;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You want regulatory guidance (CDSCO, FDA) built into your development process from day one</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#3B6D11;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You're willing to be physically present on the BIU campus for core program milestones</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 1rem;\">\u2717 Consider a different track if\u2026</h3>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#A32D2D;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2717</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You already have a working product with early revenue \u2014 the Accelerator is a better fit</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#A32D2D;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2717</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">Your innovation is primarily in Ayurveda or traditional medicine \u2014 apply for the Ayush track</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#A32D2D;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2717</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You're looking for a co-working space or a short-term mentorship programme</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#A32D2D;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2717</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You haven't yet spent meaningful time with the clinical problem and the patients it affects</span></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Phases -->\n    <p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">Curriculum</p>\n    <h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:300;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.5rem;\">12 months. Four phases. Zero shortcuts.</h2>\n    <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0 0 2.5rem;\">The program is structured in four sequential phases, each with defined deliverables. You don't move to the next phase until the current one is complete and reviewed.</p>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1.2rem;margin-bottom:5rem;\">\n      <div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <div style=\"background:#08122A;padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;\">\n    <span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.5;\">1</span>\n    <div><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;\">Months 1\u20132</div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#FFFFFF;\">Discovery & Problem Validation</div></div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:1.5rem;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:#4A5C78;margin:0 0 1rem;\">Clinical immersion, problem statement refinement, initial market assessment. You'll spend the first two months in BIU's hospital wards and OPDs.</p>\n    <div style=\"border-top:1px solid #EDE8DE;padding-top:1rem;\"><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Validated Problem Statement</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Stakeholder Interview Report</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Competitive Landscape Map</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Regulatory Pathway Scoping</div></div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n      <div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <div style=\"background:#08122A;padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;\">\n    <span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.5;\">2</span>\n    <div><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;\">Months 3\u20137</div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#FFFFFF;\">Build & Prototype</div></div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:1.5rem;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:#4A5C78;margin:0 0 1rem;\">The longest phase. Full access to BIU's biotech, pharma, and medical device labs. You'll build, test, fail, and iterate \u2014 with technical advisors at every step.</p>\n    <div style=\"border-top:1px solid #EDE8DE;padding-top:1rem;\"><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Working Prototype / MVP</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Lab Test Reports</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 IP Assessment</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Technical Specification</div></div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n      <div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <div style=\"background:#08122A;padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;\">\n    <span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.5;\">3</span>\n    <div><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;\">Months 8\u201310</div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#FFFFFF;\">Validate & Regulate</div></div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:1.5rem;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:#4A5C78;margin:0 0 1rem;\">Clinical validation with real patients through BIU's hospital. Regulatory filing preparation begins. IP protection strategy finalised.</p>\n    <div style=\"border-top:1px solid #EDE8DE;padding-top:1rem;\"><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Clinical Validation Report</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 CDSCO / FDA Filing Draft</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Patent Filing (if applicable)</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Regulatory Pathway Confirmed</div></div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n      <div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <div style=\"background:#08122A;padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;\">\n    <span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.5;\">4</span>\n    <div><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;\">Months 11\u201312</div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#FFFFFF;\">Demo Day & Launch</div></div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:1.5rem;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:#4A5C78;margin:0 0 1rem;\">Investor presentations, partnership introductions, go-to-market execution. You leave with an investor deck, pilot customers, and introductions to our investor network.</p>\n    <div style=\"border-top:1px solid #EDE8DE;padding-top:1rem;\"><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Investor Deck</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Demo Day Pitch</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 GTM Strategy</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\">\u2192 Investor Introductions</div></div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- CTA -->\n    <div style=\"background:#08122A;border-radius:4px;padding:3rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:2rem;\">\n      <div><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:300;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 0.5rem;\">Ready to apply for the Medtech Incubation track?</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);margin:0;\">Applications are rolling. Earlier is better \u2014 we spend more time with early applicants.</p></div>\n      <a href=\"/apply/\" style=\"background:#C49A2A;color:#08122A;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:2px;text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap;\">Apply for This Track \u2192</a>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>"
            },
            "elements": [],
            "widgetType": "html"
          }
        ],
        "isInner": false
      }
    ],
